# mem-constant (project-local)

This project was scaffolded with **`mem-constant init`**. Canonical specs live under **`docs/mem-constant/`** (copied from the installed package version).

## Authority

- **MemPalace** (or your chosen archive): durable facts and decisions.
- **Working cache** (e.g. Claude Mem): short-horizon thread continuity.

## Sync

Reconcile at **new chat**, **new agent**, and **end of milestone**: promote what stays true into the archive; trim the cache.

## Handoff

When context rolls over, use the **global handoff** format in `docs/mem-constant/global-handoff-template.md` (user says `handoff` or equivalent).
